{"tid":547690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(男方一直沉默)  巴西索模Bruna戀陳偉霆   強國Fans向中國政府告御狀","createTime":"2018-02-01T16:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T14:41:53.000Z","uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"404a25e20991c5c325aeeea91c7597db73815283","tid":547690,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:36:21.000Z","msg":"去咗大陸發展嘅陳偉霆（William），終於搣甩「而我不知&hellip;&hellip;」呢個稱號，仲喺大陸好受歡迎，支持者無數。<br />\n<br />\n陳偉霆被眼利嘅網民發現，同巴西索模Bruna Marth有好多共同點，有同一件衫，抱住相同狗仔等等，拍拖之說甚囂塵上。Bruna甚至將發展基地移師地香港，拉近兩人距離，又有報道話見到陳偉霆帶Bruna見家長，去到淺水灣同陳媽媽食飯。<br />\n<br />\n但就咁，正如啱啱所講，陳偉霆有好多支持者，有部份人可能因愛成恨，日日，係日日，去到Bruna嘅ig瘋狂留言，起埋佢底寫埋佢喺香港住邊。<br />\n<br />\n文字，係用簡體中文，一面倒咁鬧，侮辱誣蔑乜都有，就連貼一張舊相，或者去紅山半島打卡，都係罪名！<br />\n<br />\n「發以前的舊圖你想表演甚麼？還在做白日夢？」<br />\n「你的所有言論，我們都已經存為證據發给了中國政府，你永遠也不能踏入内地半步！很快，你也會失去香港的工作，滾回巴西了！」<br />\n「對威廉（William）來說，你已經成了過去式。」<br />\n「偏偏要惹上不該惹的事，又沒人看得起你，何必呢。」<br />\n「想要騙威廉的錢，還想借助威廉出名！！！」<br />\n「Bruna讓他浪費了很多錢，讓他的代言商和公司都不满意，讓他錯過了新的代言和電視劇。一個不能幫男人賺錢的女人，在中國，就是災難。」<br />\n<br />\n以上言論，幾乎每個留言都有，不過Bruna日前出席活動，都有讚陳偉霆靚仔、好男仔，係佢鍾意個type，但背好model answer，一問到兩人關係只會答我哋係好朋友.<br />\n<br />\n其實陳偉霆嘅「忠粉」又唔使咁嬲住喎，始終佢都冇認拍拖，咁就針對人，有失公平啫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/003553_433d08e41ad8fad3ca2f7856481d06ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F003553_433d08e41ad8fad3ca2f7856481d06ed.jpg&h=0637eb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/003553_9b2dcec361f26c81e5596e3f978b6d22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F003553_9b2dcec361f26c81e5596e3f978b6d22.jpg&h=34d6e186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/003554_cd77f137033538464d79f1853acc5d02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F003554_cd77f137033538464d79f1853acc5d02.jpg&h=3a3f9522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/003554_b5b35d7c6e03d76d09c115564f707510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F003554_b5b35d7c6e03d76d09c115564f707510.jpg&h=81663a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/003555_df8b8ed84942938e89ce688406b2e5f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F003555_df8b8ed84942938e89ce688406b2e5f6.jpg&h=bb3cfa0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4df6fe1d7a23e4a2773a50c109ff1e616b3faba","tid":547690,"uid":41508,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b0788c785568aa1d3446bb1599b1036aeb39e06","tid":547690,"uid":131259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"依啲女屌番一年半載就可以飛得"},{"pid":"aa189a9f8b0bab447478a3dbc0a7e6c76ec4d8de","tid":547690,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:34:03.000Z","msg":"邊個來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過"},{"pid":"97809c56b7070d98003e4ba41737e5b474a81bf7","tid":547690,"uid":116967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"連d fans都衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb27b0ba7ad76d6f60c2614634b744cbffcba0ff","tid":547690,"uid":53498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"支那人就係咁,遲下迫你嫁韓紅"},{"pid":"fdc2cfe305a5396880db5f11b382ceecf927166d","tid":547690,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"佢d大陸fans真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e576c00282e73176b46a8bd2be7f5a681